  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, IDynamicSimulation, DynamicDevice, MachineController, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractChildAnnotateController, AnnotateExciter, AnnotateGovernor, AnnotateStabilizer

    public abstract class AbstractAnnotateController
extends MachineControllerImpl
    Base class for all annotated CML controller - the fieldWrapperList contains a list of CML field annotation wrapper. The actual simulation is delegated to the CML filed, which is represented by a controller block, such as a DelayControlBlock - it could be child controller, represented as a CML field
